✨ DIY Boutonnière Tutorial for Your Tucson Wedding! ✨

Hey, Tucson couples! As a wedding photographer, I love capturing all the beautiful details of your special day, and a boutonnière is a perfect touch for the groom and groomsmen! Here’s a quick guide on how to create a stunning boutonnière that complements your wedding theme. 

**What You’ll Need:**
- Fresh flowers (like roses, succulents, or local blooms)
- Green floral tape
- Floral wire
- Scissors
- Ribbon (optional for a finishing touch)

**Steps to Create Your Boutonnière:**
1. **Choose Your Flowers**: Select a small flower or two that match your wedding colors. Local Tucson florists can provide beautiful options!
 
2. **Prepare the Stems**: Trim the stems to about 2-3 inches long. Remove any leaves that will sit below the pin.

3. **Wire the Flowers**: Use floral wire to secure the flowers together. Wrap the wire around the stems and twist it to hold them in place.

4. **Wrap with Floral Tape**: Starting from the base of the flowers, wrap the stems tightly with floral tape to create a clean look.

5. **Add Ribbon (Optional)**: For a touch of elegance, wrap a ribbon around the stems and tie it in a knot or bow.

6. **Pin It On**: Use a straight pin to attach the boutonnière to the lapel of the suit.

Creating your own boutonnière adds a personal touch to your Tucson wedding!  

As a Tucson wedding photographer, I love capturing these special details that make your day unique. If you’re looking for someone to document your love story, let’s connect! ✨

Reflection is the best thing that came out during this pandemic. We were all forced to slow down and process everything before us. There was no longer a “I’ll get to it tomorrow,” because that opportunity now boldly faced us.

I thought about so many parts of Happily Pink, and how I could pivot my content calendar to best serve you and our community. Then I reflected on the journey that Happily Pink has brought me on.

It’s transformed so much from the blog I started out of college. Last fall, I made the decision to invest in a more modern website. Then a few weeks ago, I finalized my new logo. I had the same website and logo for over four years so it was time for a refresh. I cannot thank @_mustbemo enough for not only creating my new logo, but also inspiring me to start Happily Pink in the first place.

On the blog, I share the logo process and the impact Mo had on Happily Pink. Head to my stories for the direct link or visit the link in my bio. Let me know what you think of the new logo!!

Bedroom 2 which can be found @healey_hall designed by @amyntawardealdam using The Recoloured collection by Charlotte Gaisford. This lovely big old Northumbrian house had a total overall and is now used as a very special and spectacular wedding accommodation. Amynta had her colour palette and she was very organised with her little book of colours. We created some great coloured wallpapers Georgie Girl storm and pinky and she wallpapered the whole of the room which looked fabulous and was quite daring considering this house was very traditional. She added lots of cushions on the beds and kept the rest of the decor simple. She didn't add too much clutter and painted most of the floors and staircases, a look that I love. Amynta was very clever at sourcing some great things for the house, she visited local auction houses, bought things from Wayfarer but looking carefully she know what would fit. I was amazed at how organised she was and how quickly this project materialised. She had used masses and masses of my wallpaper and fabrics and transformed lots of bedrooms and bathrooms. She really did all my designs justice and I was so proud to see them put together in such an original and artistic way. If you ever need a good designer for a big project ask @amyntawardealdam she would do an exceptional job for you. #healeybarn #healeyhall #weddingvenue #northumberlandwedding #charlottegaisford  #wallpaperdesigner #wallpaperdecor #geometricwallpaper #fabricstore #bespokecushions #cushionstyle #bedroomdecor #trimmings

Textured and fresh. A modern wedding invitation suite that features luxury print methods and embellishments. From white foil press printing and blind embossed details, to handmade paper, fine art prints, and unique wax seals.

How long does it take to design and produce invitations like this 

What’s your guess? 

Here’s a break down:

⌛️Client enquiries, quoting and booking: 1.5hrs
⌚️Design brief: 1.5-2hrs
⏱️Three original design concepts for the full suite (including colour concepts and all wording): 10hrs
⌛️All Revisions and client correspondence: 4hrs
⌚️Mock ups and test prints: 1hr
⏱️Spec for production (inc personalization): 2.5hrs
⌛️Order stock: 1hr
⌚️Wait for stock: 1-3 weeks
⏱️Additional test prints and final spec adjustments: 1hr
⌛️Printing and cutting: 8hrs
⌚️Assembly: 3hrs
⏱️Packaging and post: 1hr

All up a fully custom suite takes around 35hours… and I’ve been doing this for years

Does this surprise you? How long do you think it would take for you to DIY?

With arms wide open i welcome any chance i could smile. The warmth of the ☀️ on my face today reminded me how much I've missed just being present and enjoying the now. I stopped walking closed my eyes, put my hand on my chest, tuned in to the sound of the wind, and took three long deep breaths. I needed them.
_
_
Things can feel really heavy right now. They can seem like there's no real end at sight. Things are changing so quickly and we've been thurst into the new way of living. It's too easy to get consumed by the  uncertainty. 
_
_
So today's reminder is to seek joy. Seek out things that make you happy. Warm your soul. Make you smile.  Weather it's taking a extra moment to close your eyes, face turned the sun, getting dressed even though you aren't visiting anyone, or making your favourite dish at home. Take little moments for yourself and your family. 
_
_
It's not selfish, it's not self-indulgent. It's necessary and you deserve it to help you feel more contented and more in control at a time where there are a Lot of things outside your control. 
_
_
So my dear fellow friends, take those moments, and savour them too. 
_
_
Wishing everyone back home a beautiful #EidulAdha

Wedding trends for 2025 - colors pt. 1 
〰️
Svadobné trendy na rok 2025 prinášajú nádhernú paletu farieb - sage green, celestial blue a pastel yellow. Tieto odtiene dokonale vyniknú vo výzdobe, na družičkovských šatách či v drobných detailoch vášho veľkého dňa ☺️

Sage green 
Prírodný, zemitý odtieň, ktorý je jemný a univerzálny. Šalviová zelená prináša svieži kontrast k tradičnej bielej a vytvára harmóniu v kombinácii s prírodnými prvkami, ako sú eukalyptus, trávy a ľanové textílie. Táto farba je dokonalou voľbou pre rustikálne, boho aj minimalistické svadby.

Celestial blue 
Táto elegantná, pokojná farba zachytáva atmosféru jasnej oblohy a jemného luxusu. Perfektne sa kombinuje so zlatými alebo striebornými akcentmi a bielymi kvetmi, čím vytvára romantické a čisté prostredie. Nebeská modrá je ideálna pre páry, ktoré milujú sofistikovanosť a ľahkosť.

Pastel yellow 
Svieža a optimistická pastel yellow je stelesnením radosti a tepla. Je ideálna pre svadby pod holým nebom, kde vynikne v kombinácii s prírodnými kvetmi a drevenými detailmi. Pastelová žltá pôsobí jemne, no zároveň dodá každej výzdobe energiu a sviežosť, akú len jar či leto dokáže priniesť.

Ktorá z týchto farieb je vašim favoritom?

When you change the way you look at things, the things you look at change. I always envisioned my wedding day being this monumental moment. Every single last detail had to be perfect. But after this year I realized the only thing that truly mattered is love. 

Our love for each other was more than an event, it was our lives coming together for a life time. We didn’t need this production of a day for it be monumental, we just needed each other. 

The intimate ceremony we had with our immediate family was beautiful in so many ways. My heart was just as full of love that day, as it would have been any other way. It was everything I needed, wanted and prayed for.

we love a messy reception. 

reception photos deserve their whole own moment, carving out some time for a room reveal & a few newlywed pics in the space you’ve often spent months if not years planning every little detail for is something I hope to see more of. brielle & brian provided no shot list & literally just wanted us to do our thing (my love language lol) I was able to truly take time in the day to be inspired & get creative and lean into different elements of the day & reception. allowing your reception to tell a story can truly elevate your gallery, which in this case was a crazy, messy, iconic & overflowing with love kind of night. 

so to my 2025 couples, consider adding in some time for reception shots & let’s chat about how we can work it into your day

“Dearest readers...” in honor of the Bridgerton’s Season 3 release, we’re sharing a wedding that truly gave “diamond of the season.” Gilded, whimsical, and regal...O&S’s wedding day paid homage to an old world feel with modern influences. The dusty blues, shades of rose and sweet lilac color palette reminded us of the iconic Bridgerton home and all of the incredible fashion we know and love on the @netflix hit. Ornate paper goods, sparkling candle light on long banquet style tables, lush pastel florals on every surface and elevated service made this day feel like a real ball! Our couple fully embraced their adoration of all of these little details, and the result was an incredibly romantic and fun celebration!

Hello 2025! We want to reintroduce ourselves: 
We are the Women Winemakers & Culinarians Foundation - a vibrant community and movement that celebrates the talent, resilience, and camaraderie of women in wine & food within Santa Barbara County. 
Rooted in Santa Barbara County’s unconventional and maverick spirit, we’ve grown into a collective that lifts each other up while inspiring the next generation of trailblazers.

It started with a spark in 2015: a bottle share among women winemakers on International Women’s Day, fueled by the belief that women here—more than 10% of the region’s winemaking talent—deserve to be recognized and celebrated. That gathering became more than an event; it became a movement, creating a space for women to connect, collaborate, and celebrate each other’s successes.

Through the years, our mission has remained the same: to foster community and amplify the voices of women across the industry. From intimate tastings to multi-day celebrations, every moment is about about connectivity, creativity, and giving back.

Together, we’ve supported causes that empower women, from farmworkers to veterans, and built a network of support that goes beyond the vineyard.

Now in 2025, we’re growing once again—adding more events and gatherings - be sure to connect with us here, drop a note too and we can connect. 

Join us as we continue to celebrate collaboration, champion community, and create a movement of supportive women shaping the future of wine & culinary!

Our hearts go out to all those impacted by the devastating Los Angeles wildfires. Since 2018 our Pink Ash rosé wine - inspired by California's resilient spirit in the face of past fires - has supported our brave first responders and the future prevention of wildfires in our Southern California community. One-third of all proceeds of our Pink Ash wine are donated directly to purchasing equipment to fight these devastating fires as well as keeping our first responders safe. 

From the ash rises strength, the nutrient to rebuild and grow again. We will continue our mission to help support our brave first responders who make incredible sacrifices running into the danger selflessly to save lives, homes, and our community.

California has wine countries all over the state but did you know there are over 200 wineries throughout Santa Barbara County? However if you’re just visiting the city of Santa Barbara like I did with @lainflight, you can still enjoy great wine in one of the many tasting rooms.

Wineries/Tasting Rooms to Check out in Santa Barbara:
    

@carrwinery
414 N Salsipuedes St - Downtown
Carr Winery offers tastings, wines by the bottle, wine to go and more. Hang out inside or in their spacious outdoor patio.

@muniwine
22 Anacapa Street - Funk Zone
Municipal Winemakers is a hip tasting room that is open daily. They offer tastings, wine by the glass, and by the bottle. Seating is limited to arrive early.

Whitcraft Winery
36 S. Calle Cesar Chavez - Funk Zone
Whitcraft Winery is one of the oldest wineries in Santa Barbara and known for their varietals of Pinot Noir, Chardonnay, and Syrah. 

@carrwinery thevalleyprojectwines
116 E. Yanonali Street - Funk Zone
Valley Project is the best place to get a “tour of some of the best Santa Barbara County wineries” all in one place. Come get a lesson on SB’s microclimates, soil and more!

@deepseawine
217 Stearns Wharf - On the Wharf
Deep Sea Wine is located on the wharf and is the best place if you’re looking for ocean views. Enjoy their premier selection of single varietals, single vineyard, hand-crafted artisanal wines.

Please welcome new member 10 Ninths Estate! 

10 Ninths Estate are located in westernmost edge of the Sta. Rita Hills. 

Deploying minimal intervention viticultural practices, 10 Ninths Estate aims to bring out vibrant, balanced, and distinctive qualities in all of their wines.

At 10 Ninths Estate, the team strives to create exceptional wines that harmonize with nature. Through regenerative methods, they nurture each vine in its native environment, yielding grapes that authentically embody the terroir's essence. 

10 Ninths Estate has big plans to expand globally, uplift communities, protect the environment, and inspire a legacy of excellence, sustainability, and mindful living.

10 Ninths Estate is making Pinot Noir, Chardonnay and Rosé of Pinot Noir from the Sta Rita Hills. 

To Shop 10 Ninths Estate - please visit their website and join their mailing list for all future brand updates.

Obliteratingly rich decadent Syrah, but not in an overwrought overripe sort of way as we are all accustomed to; More of an I must decant this, green, spicy, brilliantly concentrated version harkening to Yorkville Highlands, where black richness elevates itself on wings of absolute perfection in Syrah translation. This comes from far south of there though, a Ballard Canyon offering somehow clamoring with all the placemarks of a decadent, thiccc California example while still managing enough ire, acid and tannin to keep the 1% on its toes. These wines are--ahockingly--very differently composed than Dusty Nabor's wines, and I would love to be a fly on the wall for conversations between winemaker and label concerning their vision. They're so different, and honestly: I might even like them better. The nose grassy and briar-ridden; The uptake abrasive and unforgiving; the middle and finish compelling and awe-inducing: grainy and complex and begging for another decade of rest. They honestly remind me of some of Qupe's finest Bien Nacido bottles. This makes Pax taste like grilled cheese sandwiches. This makes Saxum taste like Austin Hope. This is hoisin to soy sauce. This is etherealy good syrah. I've said some bad things about Ballard Canyon in my life, but this is where it's at boys & girls.

I identify as a sex-positive feminist. This means that, for me, sexual freedom is closely tied to my belief in gender equality and personal freedom, and that sex/sexuality has the ability to empower me both individually and in my relationships. It brings me physical pleasure, inspires acceptance in my body, and gives me both a positive self-image and a deeper understanding of self. 

As things change on this platform I’m not entirely sure when I and people like me are going to be allowed to exist. After years of fighting for my body to have the same liberties as everyone else I find myself at a harsh crossroads. The works still isn’t done, and my time here might be up. Whether I want it to be or not. 

So, if you like what I have to say, what I do, how I do it. Please sign up for my new mailing list so that years of emotional labor and love was not for nothing. Thank you for being here. 

<3 Megan

Можно ли действительно избавиться от первых морщинок?

Первое появление морщин часто становится поводом задуматься о состоянии своей кожи. Многие считают, что с ними невозможно справиться, но это не совсем так! Современная косметология предлагает решения, которые помогут не только замедлить их появление, но и уменьшить уже существующие.

 Почему появляются первые морщинки?
Морщины образуются из-за естественной потери эластичности кожи, снижения выработки коллагена и гиалуроновой кислоты. Плохая экология, стресс, неправильное питание и активная мимика только ускоряют этот процесс.

 Какие процедуры помогут справиться с первыми морщинами?

1️⃣ Биоревитализация
Это инъекции гиалуроновой кислоты, которые восстанавливают уровень увлажнённости кожи, делают её более упругой и здоровой. Процедура особенно эффективна для тех, кто замечает первые признаки обезвоженности и мелкие морщины.

2️⃣ VL26G
Инновационная процедура с пептидами, которые стимулируют выработку коллагена. Это отличный способ улучшить текстуру кожи, уменьшить мелкие заломы и продлить молодость.

3️⃣ Коктейль Монако
Комплекс активных веществ, который помогает бороться с тусклым цветом лица, первыми морщинками и улучшает общее состояние кожи. Процедура оказывает выраженный омолаживающий эффект и подходит для профилактики возрастных изменений.

4️⃣ Ботокс
Идеально подходит для работы с мимическими морщинами. Если вы замечаете заломы в области лба, между бровями или вокруг глаз, ботокс поможет расслабить мышцы и сделать кожу гладкой.

 Какой результат можно ожидать?
Эти процедуры не просто уменьшают морщины, но и помогают поддерживать естественную красоту и здоровье кожи. При регулярном уходе и соблюдении рекомендаций косметолога, кожа становится более упругой, свежей и ухоженной.

Избавиться от первых морщинок действительно можно, если начать вовремя заботиться о своей коже. Современные процедуры не только устраняют мелкие дефекты, но и предотвращают появление новых. Главное – вовремя обратиться к специалисту и найти тот метод, который будет максимально эффективным именно для вас.

✨ Un Matrimonio da Sogno alla Tonnara di Scopello ✨

Immaginate un angolo di paradiso dove il mare cristallino bacia la roccia, dove la storia e la natura si fondono in un’armonia unica. La Tonnara di Scopello, con la sua vista mozzafiato e il fascino senza tempo, è stata la cornice perfetta per un matrimonio italiano che rimarrà nel cuore di tutti.

Abbiamo creato insieme a una coppia speciale un’esperienza indimenticabile, dal primo incontro alla giornata più importante. Con la nostra cura e attenzione per ogni dettaglio, abbiamo trasformato il sogno di un matrimonio in realtà, dove eleganza, tradizione e la bellezza della Sicilia si sono incontrati.

Se desideri un matrimonio che parli di te, delle tue radici e della tua storia d’amore, la Tonnara di Scopello è il luogo che fa per te. Noi, come wedding planner, siamo qui per rendere ogni tuo desiderio realtà, curando ogni aspetto del grande giorno con passione e dedizione.

Contattaci per scoprire come possiamo creare il tuo matrimonio perfetto!

Ti riporta via come la marea la felicità...

Sono una romanticona con una sensibilità spiccata! Ogni tanto mi piace condividere un po’ di sano romanticismo...Concedetemelo!  

Da una perfetta Disney addicted e instancabile sognatrice come me, amante di castelli, principi, principesse e fiabe dal lieto fine...dovreste pur aspettarvelo!  

Fra qualche giorno io e mio marito faremo 10 anni che ci conosciamo e anche quasi 10 che stiamo insieme...eppure a me sembra sia passato molto meno! Perché quando stai bene con una persona il tempo passa in fretta! 

Amiamo gente! E diciamolo ogni volta che ci viene dal cuore!
Ma soprattutto dimostriamolo, anche con piccoli gesti, ogni giorno! Con un bacio in fronte, una colazione portata a letto, un abbraccio spontaneo, un dolcino sulla scrivania. L’Amore ha bisogno di essere alimentato sempre! Perché sentirselo dire è bello, ma vederselo dimostrare cambia tutto! ❤️

Mangia, mangia! One of the first questions everyone has around our wedding is about the altar and decor decisions. When the insanely talented @m_woodcock and @ezrawoodsofficial of @pretendplantsandflowers asked what we were thinking for the flowers we replied that we were, in fact, thinking...no flowers.
.
In lieu of traditional floral arrangements, we hand selected a cornucopia of Sicilian produce from a local wholesaler on the mainland and ferried it over to the island by boat. We feel so lucky to have such brilliant besties who collaborated to bring our vision to life. While Michael and Ezra were leading the creative charge, it was also our community of helpful friends who came together to actualize the drippy tomatoes at the altar, stacks of juicy peaches on the Moorish heads and braids of garlic and more cascading from the tables.  
.
Watching the tomato altar come to life from our bathroom window (haha, it had the best view of the action!!) on the top floor was pure magic, and seeing the tables for the first time left us in awe. We never thought we’d care about this stuff because we’d never seen versions of the details that we were truly excited about, but we were blown away by how @pretendplantsandflowers turned this bounty of local fruits and vegetables into sculptures of color and texture.
.
From the bottom of our hearts, thank you to everyone who hustled up til the last moment, who somehow stacked carrots into a delicate tower, and who had to let their hair air dry crazy in the hot Sicilian sun because they spent all their time building out our wonderful wedding landscape instead of saving time to blow dry their hair.  We felt so celebrated and supported by your colorful contributions to our most meaningful day.
.
The next morning at breakfast, the hotel served the prickly pears and other produce from the night before for breakfast. It all tasted perfect. And yes, Michael made my bouquet of sparkling lemons with pearl nips and drips. It was the best!
.
To those tagged, we love you all infinitely!✨

Ein Hauch von Liebe in jeder Flasche! 

Stell dir vor: Deine Gäste sitzen an liebevoll gedeckten Tischen, das warme Licht schafft eine magische Atmosphäre, und vor jedem Platz steht ein kleines Geschenk – eine elegante Flasche Rosenwasser mit einer zarten Kunstrosenblüte darin.

Dieses kleine Detail erzählt eine Geschichte: von Wertschätzung, von Erinnerungen, die bleiben, und von einem Moment, der über den Tag hinaus strahlt.

✨ Das Besondere an unseren Gastgeschenken:
Jede Flasche ist nicht nur ein Geschenk, sondern eine Botschaft. Das Rosenwasser, inspiriert von Tradition und Eleganz, wird begleitet von einer Kunstrosenblüte, die nie verblüht – genau wie die Erinnerung an deinen besonderen Tag.

Ob Hochzeit, Taufe oder Jubiläum – mit diesen kleinen Kunstwerken zeigst du deinen Gästen, wie viel sie dir bedeuten.

 Lass uns deine Geschichte erzählen!

 Her Şişede Sevgi Saklı! 

Hayal edin: Misafirleriniz özenle hazırlanmış masalarda oturuyor, sıcak bir ışık ortamı büyülü kılıyor ve her tabağın yanında küçük bir hediye – zarif bir şişe gül suyu, içinde narin bir yapay gül çiçeğiyle.

Bu küçük detay bir hikâye anlatıyor: Minnettarlık, kalıcı anılar ve o özel günün ötesine uzanan bir güzellik hikâyesi.

✨ Hediyelerimizin Farkı:
Her şişe sadece bir hediye değil, aynı zamanda bir mesaj. Gelenek ve zarafetten ilham alan gül suyu, asla solmayan yapay bir gül çiçeğiyle birlikte sunuluyor – tıpkı o özel günün hatıraları gibi.

The i9 and i7 are both high-performance processor lines from Intel, but they cater to different needs and offer distinct features. Here’s a brief comparison:

Intel Core i7:

- Typically offers 6-8 cores and 12-16 threads
- High-performance for gaming, content creation, and heavy multitasking
- Hyper-Threading technology for improved multithreading
- Generally more affordable than i9 processors
- Suitable for most users who need a powerful processor for demanding tasks

Intel Core i9:

- Offers 8-18 cores and 16-36 threads
- Extreme performance for:
 - Professional content creators (video editing, 3D modeling)
 - Heavy data processing and analytics
 - Extreme gaming and streaming
- Higher Turbo Boost frequencies for increased single-thread performance
- Supports more PCIe lanes and memory channels for enhanced expandability
- Generally more expensive than i7 processors
- Ideal for professionals and enthusiasts who require the absolute best performance

Key differences:

- Core count: i9 typically offers more cores and threads than i7
- Performance: i9 provides higher Turbo Boost frequencies and better multithreading capabilities
- Price: i9 processors are generally more expensive than i7 processors
- Use case: i9 is suited for extreme workloads and professional applications, while i7 is suitable for most high-performance needs

Remember, the specific differences between i9 and i7 processors can vary depending on the generation and model. Always check the specifications and benchmarks for the particular processor you’re interested in.

The i9 and i7 are both high-performance processor lines from Intel, but they cater to different needs and offer distinct features. Here's a brief comparison:

Intel Core i7:

- Typically offers 6-8 cores and 12-16 threads
- High-performance for gaming, content creation, and heavy multitasking
- Hyper-Threading technology for improved multithreading
- Generally more affordable than i9 processors
- Suitable for most users who need a powerful processor for demanding tasks

Intel Core i9:

- Offers 8-18 cores and 16-36 threads
- Extreme performance for:
 - Professional content creators (video editing, 3D modeling)
 - Heavy data processing and analytics
 - Extreme gaming and streaming
- Higher Turbo Boost frequencies for increased single-thread performance
- Supports more PCIe lanes and memory channels for enhanced expandability
- Generally more expensive than i7 processors
- Ideal for professionals and enthusiasts who require the absolute best performance

Key differences:

- Core count: i9 typically offers more cores and threads than i7
- Performance: i9 provides higher Turbo Boost frequencies and better multithreading capabilities
- Price: i9 processors are generally more expensive than i7 processors
- Use case: i9 is suited for extreme workloads and professional applications, while i7 is suitable for most high-performance needs

Remember, the specific differences between i9 and i7 processors can vary depending on the generation and model. Always check the specifications and benchmarks for the particular processor you're interested in.

이번에 Blanc101에서 출시한 
라딥 솔리드 퍼퓸이에요.
처음으로 선보이는 제품인데요. 
먼저 한번 써봤어요

우선 Ladeep은 라벤더로 스트레스를 완화하고 
안정을 주는 향으로
특히 저녁에 바르고 나면 숙면에 도움을 준다고 해요.

제형은 반투명한 타입이지만
바르는 순간 스르륵 스며들어버려서 
촉촉함이 우선 좋더라구요.
처음에는 핸드크림이라고 착각할만한데 
라딥 솔리드 퍼퓸은 고체 향수에요 ㅎㅎ

손에 바르고 오후 내내 사용해 봤는데
은은하게 계속 유지되더라구요!

과하지 않은 향이라 부담 없었고
끈적임이 없어서 좋았어요

핸드크림이나 이런 고체 향수가 
끈적임이 많은 제품라인도 있는지라
개인적으로 만족스럽더라구요!

그리고 에탄올은 0% 첨가되어 있고
알라토인, 히알루론산, 판테놀 이 3가지 성분이 
수분 손실 없이 보습효과와 부드러운 
영양감을 주는 성분이라고 해요!

특히 아주 쌀쌀해진 올가을에 은은하게 
지속되는 향과 촉촉함이 딱 어울리는 것 같아요

Blanc101에서 바디워시부터 바디로션은 물론이고
핸드워시랑 페브릭 세탁세제와 섬유 유연제 등
다양하게 나오니까 들어가서 한번 살펴보세요!

#제품제공

주안이 태어날때 부터 사용한 세제 블랑 101에서 신제품이 출시됬어요. 

바로 샤벳처럼 스르르 녹는 블랑의 신제품 라딥 솔리드퍼퓸 고체향수예요. 

지금 둘째를 임신은 했지만 일을 하는 엄마라 출근할때 약간의 향기는 필요한데 향수는 못 뿌리겠더라구요. 
그런 저에게 이제품이 아주 찰떡이예요. 

라딥 솔리드 퍼퓸은 에탄올 0% 라서 더욱 안심하고 사용이 가능하고 샤벳처럼 끈적임 없이 발라지는데 향은 은은한 라벤더향이 오래 지속되어서 너무 기분 좋았어요. 

목 뒤나, 손목, 쇄골부위에 발라주시면되고, 핸드크림 대용으로도 사용가능하니 선물용으로도 너무 좋은 제품이에요. 
자기전에도 살짝 발라주면 잠도 잘오고 좋네요. 

은은한 블랑101의 라딥 솔리드퍼퓸 고체향수 강추

라딥 솔리드퍼퓸은 고체향수로 사르르 녹는 샤벳 제형이에요.ᐟ 손에 적당량을 덜어서 손목, 쇄골, 목 등에 발라주면 되는데 영양감이 있어서 핸드크림으로도 사용할 수 있어요(* ॑ᵕ ॑* )♡

︰LADEEP [라딥]
라벤더로 스트레스를 완화하고 마음의 안정을 주어 수면의 질을 높여주는데 도움을 주는 향

요즘 깊게 잠들지 못하고 자꾸 깨는데 라딥은 숙면에 도움을 주는 향이라서 바르고 자면 편안해지고 깊게 잠들 수 있을 것 같아요˶•⩊•˶.ᐟ

✔️고급스러운 향을 원하는 사람

블랑101 솔리드퍼퓸 라딥은 
라벤더향이 은은하게 나고 중성적인 부드러운향이다. 
향수처럼 톡쏘는 듯한 느낌이 없어 자극적이지 않은향이라 
부담없이 바를 수 있고 제형이 샤베트처럼 부드러워 
바르는 느낌이 참 좋다. 
잔향이 살냄새 느낌이라 바디로션이나 워시로 나와도 좋을거 같은 제품

#BLANC101
너무나 좋아하는 브랜드 블랑101
시그니처향, 멜로우바닐라향을 즐겨 사용하며 세탁의 즐거움을 알게해준 고마운 브랜드 인데요!

이번에 좋은 기회로 블랑의 신제품 라딥 솔리드퍼퓸을 사용해보았어요

샤벳처럼 사르르 녹아들어 부드럽게 피부에 흡수되고
오랫동안 편안한 향을 유지하는 고체향수랍니다

아로마로 스트레스를 완화하고 마음의 안정을 주어 숙면할수있도록 도와주는 향이라고 해요

라벤더, 자스민, 프리지아 향이 어우러져 은은하고 산뜻하며
정말 마음이 편안해지는 향이더라구요 
(향이 좋아서 자꾸 맡고싶은 킁킁☺️)

겨울에 포근한 이불속에 쏙 들어가있는 그런 기분이 드는 향이랍니다‍️

고체향수라 혹시나 독하거나 끈적일까 걱정했는데
전혀 자극적이지않고 너무 촉촉하고 뽀송한 마무리가 참 인상적이었어요

포장 디자인도 너무 감각있고 용기도 위생적으로 사용하기 좋아서 부담없는 선물용으로 좋겠어요
